Lightning General Contracting 
                 
WE MAKE DREAMS REALITY!!

We build – that’s our passion. 
Construction is not easy – but we love to do it with ease.
We are destined to construct your dream. 
Need to build your dream? Call us!
Construction is complicated...we are not!

We work hard to materialize your dream. 
We are proud to construct the future of the nation.
We can play with many new ideas to create something special.

We have skills to make your every dream real with our great teamwork.
We have various skills to work as a successful builder of both Residential and Commercial property's. 
We are good at changing your dream into the existing reality.

We are knowledgeable about the durability of any building material.
We are detail-oriented people while we work on our projects.

Great buildings are given shape by us.
We are here to work hard and bring your dream into reality.
We shape the buildings and then they shape our lives.

profile:
WOODLINE Corporation has been established and registered since 2015 as a Custom Framing Company. The WOODLINE Team provides services in framing custom homes, basements, decks, home additions, pergolas and sheds as well as custom architectural metal work.

All projects are delivered with quality, care and within budget. WOODLINE strives to complete all projects whether big or small on time, and under the careful planning of our experienced Project Manager with 15 years experience in the construction industry.

Our employees are highly skilled with over 12 years experience in the House Framing Industry. We continue to upgrade and stay competitive within industry standards.
services: Framing Custom Homes, Home Additions, Basements, Pergolas, Sheds and Custom Architectural Metal Work.
